title: Dunk Low SB 'AM90 Infrared'
description: The Dunk Low SB 'AM90 Infrared' celebrates the 30th anniversary of the Air Max 90 by borrowing the retro runner’s iconic OG color scheme. The low-top features a predominantly grey suede upper with black leather on the heel overlay and breathable white mesh at the toe box and collar. Contrasting pops of Infrared appear at the tongue, heel tab and rubber outsole.
